    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The engine and transmission are functional, though you may notice some minor fluid seepage and a suspension that feels a bit aged. Externally, the paint shows its age with some fading on the hood and a few noticeable door dings and scratches. The interior is intact but shows clear signs of wear on the upholstery and some cracked plastic trim. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that runs and drives, but it isn't a showpiece and will eventually require some routine maintenance to keep it in top shape.",
